article:
'Natalie' is a female given name derived from Late Latin name [[Natalia (given
name)|Natalia]] meaning "Christmas Day" (cf. Latin natale domini).
http://www.behindthename.com/name/natalie This form is found in many
languages but especially common in French and English speaking countries.

* Natalie Alvarado (commonly referred to as "Natalie"), American R&B singer
